{"tid":1885561,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"留低你最寶貴既回憶","createTime":"2020-02-18T11:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T11:50:13.000Z","uid":334755,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9bdcc6916b1ee4d3759d60d6854cac694b6088","tid":1885561,"uid":334755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"細細個身體好差，成日因為哮喘入急症。小學請假個頁滿曬。食好多野都會嘔，又咳到死，基本上成日要在張床休息。個時姑姐日日照顧我，又會燉蘋果比我食。好辛苦，但都係我最寶貴既回憶。以前仲會同姑姐一齊去泥灘玩，踏單車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想聽大家最寶貴既回憶。<br />\n利申:媽媽早逝，姑姐照顧到我中學。然後跟番爸爸住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b1e0c01197754a520bae0387dfe7813ff94d47","tid":1885561,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"樓主願你做個善良的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6a369d4ea7edc08feb07b5c95a37fab8387cb4","tid":1885561,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"留名睇鬥慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0f1b47fe959c9f85d84b5598c00c0bb1379e5c","tid":1885561,"uid":13391,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"細個老豆老母唔喺身邊，得我婆婆照顧。有晚半夜發高燒，我婆婆揹我去醫院睇醫生，印象中仲記得佢背脊濕曬同喘氣。<br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生要留院，瞓到下晝先起身，發現佢仲坐喺我隔離，一早買咗粉比我食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢幾年前過咗身啦，但我仲係好掛住佢，有時發夢都會見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7158940fbe66a6aed12f36c7148d6ad8db34bb90","tid":1885561,"uid":334755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b1e0c01197754a520bae0387dfe7813ff94d47","tid":1885561,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"樓主願你做個善良的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"善良呀 大個就好左好多 哮喘無事了"},{"pid":"2aa0eb94d73a0ae9ac658d75e55ce99c3efa954e","tid":1885561,"uid":334755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d6a369d4ea7edc08feb07b5c95a37fab8387cb4","tid":1885561,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"留名睇鬥慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"寶貴回憶 唔慘啦 諗番都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcc179def0269a8cc00d66d8cf4da5710d3aeae","tid":1885561,"uid":334755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb0f1b47fe959c9f85d84b5598c00c0bb1379e5c","tid":1885561,"uid":13391,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"細個老豆老母唔喺身邊，得我婆婆照顧。有晚半夜發高燒，我婆婆揹我去醫院睇醫生，印象中仲記得佢背脊濕曬同喘氣。<br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生要留院，瞓到下晝先起身，發現佢仲坐喺我隔離，一早買咗粉比我食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢幾年前過咗身啦，但我仲係好掛住佢，有時發夢都會見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"婆婆好錫你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你都一定好掛住佢 先會發夢都見到佢 真係要好好珍惜身邊既人"},{"pid":"d0ff016746677aa6b070ef856438928ee9e77414","tid":1885561,"uid":334755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7453ac8a25a5725f3084bbf4799f91bd74c511c","tid":1885561,"uid":186662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"細個時候同兩個家姐一齊玩多啦a夢大富翁 <br />\n佢地個時好錫我 但大個左就關係就無咁close 可能歲數問題  一個差10年 一個差7年"},{"pid":"c52b969c45f1f21fa60e61d4bb985e39c8f35ee6","tid":1885561,"uid":334755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7453ac8a25a5725f3084bbf4799f91bd74c511c","tid":1885561,"uid":186662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:28:12.